      <p><font face="Arial,Helvetica"><font size="+2">Green letter against green 
        background that is distinguished in (a) nothing, (b) lightness (not brightness!), 
        (c) saturation, (d) lightness and saturation.</font></font> </p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
</ul>
